title: Star Trek the next generation Season 6 episode 4 fanedit
description:
This is the episode with Scotty in it. 

I never liked this episode simply because the show focused on how old the engineer was. On how things have moved on. 

Instead of giving us a good sci-fi episode, we got treated to a show that made the old fans of star trek feel old. 

Now, this focus is gone. 

No-one gets on his case cause everything has moved on, just Scotty himself. In a touching scene on the holodeck with Captian Picard. 

Geordi La Forge is no longer an ass to Scotty. 

May the Trek be with you
